      "content": "hey i've been having such a hard time sleeping lately like im tossing and turning all night. i already take a bit of melatonin every night but it isnt really doing much anymore. my doctor gave me some zolpidem (ambien) a while back for when things get bad, can i just take the melatonin and the zolpidem at the same time to make sure i actually pass out? would that be okay?",
